snippet: The choreographer Pavel Zustiak’s “Strange Cargo,” the final part of his “Painted Bird” trilogy, is being performed through Sunday at the Cathedral Church of St. John the Divine.
abstract: Gia Kourlas reviews premiere performance of Pavel Zustiak dance Strange Cargo, the final section of his Painted Bird trilogy, at Synod Hall.
lead_paragraph: The choreographer Pavel Zustiak’s “Strange Cargo,” the final part of his “Painted Bird” trilogy, is being performed through Sunday at the Cathedral Church of St. John the Divine.

headline.seo: Zustiak’s ‘Strange Cargo,’ at St. John the Divine
